                    "line_text": "Pour l'œil qui sait voir les larmes des choses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ce banc désert regrette le passé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Les longs baisers et le bouquet de roses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
